The pixel 4 gestures work essentially every time for me. That being said, I don't use them often, BUT!! They use the soli sensor to better detect when I'm about to pickup my phone, which can fire up the face unlock sensors way faster, making this the fastest face unlock I've ever seen, and frankly the fastest unlock that I've personally used.

So just for that, I really hope the sensor sticks around and has some new features
